TOPICS: ToD vs GhostGGGL beef, Napo ban cycle, grimfoLf streamcheating accusations, tower griefing meta, mubarak necro drama
DRAMA: ToD. GhostGGGL. No Eyes. Towers. War. | ToD and GhostGGGL feuded all week straight. Started Monday with tower mocking. Escalated through Friday with physical threats and character assassination. Both accused each other of griefing. By end of week they were trading reports and promising vendettas. "ToD: lynfan no spikes ghost no towers lynfan no towers" "GhostGGGL: Tod no eyes blocked by the nose" "GhostGGGL: Suck my dick" "ToD: so u would see i told u to make towers"; Napo banned twice in one week for leaving games with workers alive "Napo: i COACHED MY SELF" "Napo: iam cooking soup later" "NAPO#21972 teamkill denied ok this is a hard one just don't leave games"; grimfoLf accused of streamcheating by GhostGGGL who claimed bat unit choices only griefed in GhostGGGL's games "GhostGGGL: You ALWAYS make bats in oppo team NEVER in my team I think you purposely grief" "GhostGGGL: And you streamcheat too" "grimfoLf: im know streamsniper and maphacker"; Sharky banned 14 days for tower griefing instead of making units "Sharky: fuck yourself" "Plasticstone: he starts with tower before hero"; zairongliu posted translated Chinese death threats mid-week "zairongliu: I WANT FUCK U MOM U LIKE RAT" then had fuetti translate threat for EYEServ
BANS: Sharky 14 days for griefing with towers only; Napo 2 days twice for leaving with workers; PeaceANDlove sabotage (lost TC on creeps, left 4:39)
HIGHLIGHTS: mubarak revealed royal family Kuwait wealth flex drawing instant cash jokes "mubarak: royal family of kuwait" "McGregor: u r rich"; volumeǃone mocked himself for winning without trying "volumeǃone: i'm not even playin still winning kappa"; Biersch1ss TC bait mind game with virgin blonde girl reference got chat talking "mubarak: bier ur tc bait me" "Biersch1ss: the tc was like 18 years old virgin blond girl"; grimfoLf and Bravid wholesome roast session mid-ladder grind "BRAVID: u suck u been griefing all day" "grimfoLf: stay salty remember to inhale ur daily dose of copium"; Onslaught and BiGToBi bonded over Audi car flex while playing "BiGToBi: that elf was like a punto 1.0" "Onslaught: i got a 330e too but soon an Audi A3 2026 being delivered"
RECAP: Week was chaos. ToD and GhostGGGL weaponized tower building as insult and excuse. Napo got banned twice for the same crime. Sharky got hit with 14-day hammer. zairongliu posted death threats that needed Chinese translation. Meanwhile mubarak revealed he owns Kuwait real estate and Unapologetic climbed 176 MMR over 70 games while Chonky dropped 199 in 4. UD picked most consistently at 51% winrate. Wednesday maxed out at 100 games. The week proved that even at high MMR, griefing accusations trump actual gameplay. Towers. Grief. Reports. Repeat.

LOSER: Chonky#11418 -199 MMR (0W-4L)
GRINDER: mubarak#22745 183 games (82W-101L)

WINNER_BLURB: Climbed +176 MMR across 70 games on HU — 67% win rate. Best day: Friday,
going 10-4. Didn't say much in English, but had some advice for        
improving your foreign language skills: 找个女老外当对象哈哈哈哈 — "find a foreign girlfriend hahaha."
LOSER_BLURB: Spent Valentine's Day playing 4 games of wc3. Lost all 4, bled 199 MMR in 2 hours, and called it a night. Some people get flowers. Chonky got -50 MMR per game. No notes.
GRINDER_BLURB: 183 games. Every single day. 36 in one sitting on Tuesday. He went
82-101 and lost 130 MMR but mubarak doesn't grind for stats — he grinds
because there's nothing else he'd rather do. Coffee, cigarettes, Marks &
Spencer pyjamas, and a real estate portfolio that funds the whole operation.
GRINDER_QUOTES: "mubarak: i am mubarak masser of games all will know my name!"; "but now im old stop holidays! holiday is food and wc3 and bed for    me"; "coffee and cigs all day with wc3"; "used to and stopped after 38y/o u tend to say f it and just wanna    live ur life"; "adapting to the ramadan schedule! incoming 50 games!"
HOTSTREAK_BLURB: Won 11 in a row. What's the secret? Ditch the Mac, hit the gym, and for 
the love of God stop typing in caps: "dont get my people keep using caps these days."
HOTSTREAK_QUOTES: "MiSTArQ: lol gaming on mac is always bad idea, not made forr it :D"; "MiSTArQ: dont get my people keep using caps these days"; "MiSTArQ: go to the gym kiddo"
COLDSTREAK_BLURB: Lost a staggering 16 games in a row. Despite the account sharing accusations, Lynfan blames lag, disconnects, and griefing allies — particularly ToD, who he accuses of stealing his MMR. But don't feel too bad for him: "no, i dont care mmr."
